[gd_scene load_steps=22 format=3 uid="uid://locale_hce_commercial_v1"]

; ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
; VOL 6 · CHAPTER ONE BASELINE · HCE Commercial Cluster
; The Kwik Stop ↔ NexCorp Gas & Go intersection per _VOL6_WIKI.md.
;
; Scene origin (0, 0, 0) = the four-way intersection center. Player
; spawns just south of it on the West Commercial Strip sidewalk so
; the first thing visible is the Kwik Stop to the west and the Gas
; & Go canopy to the east — Sam's register on the left, Skip's
; pumps on the right.
;
; Lighting BASE is tuned for Texas noon (per _LIGHTING_PLAYBOOK.md's
; "tune base lighting for the scene's primary hour" rule). F11
; cycles other hours from there. Practicals (sodium streetlight
; heads, canopy underlights, interior bulbs) sit at night-rated
; values so the F11 → midnight transition pumps them up cleanly.
; ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

