; ── KEY LIGHTS — three-light foundation, Texas noon base ─────────
; Sun_Key matched to MoodCycler's "_Key" suffix → F11 sun rotation.
; Energies sit at HCE-noon levels (4.5 / 0.9 / 1.6) so the F11
; cycle has room to dim them for golden/blue/night without
; bottoming out.
